title: Warped!
overview: Warped! follows Milo, the beloved head geek and manager at a popular comic book store whose microcosm is disrupted when his boss hires the loud and excitable, Ruby. Despite their differences, the two form an unlikely alliance when they team up to create the next great graphic novel with friends, Hurley, the pizza worker next door, and Darby, who dreams of opening her own fashion line.Â
